@startuml
title Time and Update - Practical Flow

skinparam ParticipantPadding 8

participant "Application update loop" as Loop
participant "Timestamp" as Timestamp
participant "Duration" as Duration
participant "UpdateTick" as Tick
participant "Timer / Chronometer" as Tools
participant "Widget" as Widget

Loop -> Timestamp : read current time
Loop -> Duration : compute elapsed time
Loop -> Tick : create update tick
Loop -> Widget : update(tick)

Widget -> Tick : read elapsed time
Widget -> Tools : advance timers
Tools -> Duration : compare thresholds
Tools --> Widget : elapsed/finished state

note bottom
Update code receives explicit time values so movement,
animation, and timers are independent from frame rate.
end note

@enduml
